&CONTROL
  calculation     = 'vc-relax',
  prefix          = 'MoS2',
  pseudo_dir      = './../pseudo',
  outdir          = './../tmp/',
  etot_conv_thr   = 1.0d-6,
  forc_conv_thr   = 1.0d-4,
/
&SYSTEM
  ibrav           = 0,
  nat             = 3,
  ntyp            = 2,
  ecutwfc         = 80,
  ecutrho         = 350,
/

&ELECTRONS
  conv_thr        = 1.0d-8,
/

&IONS
  ion_dynamics    = 'bfgs',
/

&CELL
  cell_dynamics   = 'bfgs',
  cell_dofree     = '2Dxy',
/

ATOMIC_SPECIES
Mo     95.95000  Mo_ONCV_PBE_sr.upf
S      32.06500  S_ONCV_PBE_sr.upf

CELL_PARAMETERS {angstrom}
  3.185300   0.000000   0.000000
 -1.592650   2.758551   0.000000
  0.000000   0.000000  20.270000

ATOMIC_POSITIONS (crystal)
Mo               0.6666664225        0.3333322010        0.1678139380
S                0.3333334793        0.6666672224        0.0906557537
S                0.3333334312        0.6666672436        0.2449733083

K_POINTS (automatic)
